title: Universe Cowards
text:
"Universe Cowards" (Korean: 우주겁쟁이; RR: Woojoo Geopjaengi), also known briefly by Universe Hipsters (Korean: 우주힙쟁이; RR: Woojoo Hipjaengi), is a musical duo consisting of Super Junior's Heechul and Buzz's Min Kyung-hoon. The duo debuted on the hit show, Knowing Bros as a project duo and released their first ever single, "Sweet Dream". The duo name is a mix of Hee-chul's nickname, "Universe Big Star" and Buzz's song, "Coward".
